IMPERIAL COLLEGE HISAR

Director’s Message

Since its establishment, Imperial College has been successfully working with its identifying motto — ‘Shiksha Bhi, Sanskar Bhi.’ At every moment, it is committed to the path of progress. In this direction, the college not only focuses on education but also imparts values to its students and provides a healthy environment for their holistic development.
